            <lg xml:id="TK142">
<l>aṟaṉkaṭai niṉṟāru ḷellām piṟaṉkaṭai</l>
<l>niṉṟāriṟ pētaiyā ril</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Among all those who stand outside dharma, none are such fools</l>
<l>as they who stand outside the door of another man.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
